Je vais t'attraper, Amy !

69
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:14,120
Non.

70
00:04:14,160 --> 00:04:15,860
Et si !

71
00:04:22,960 --> 00:04:24,390
Maia...

72
00:04:25,170 --> 00:04:26,530
Maia, ca va ?

73
00:04:26,770 --> 00:04:27,880
Ca fait mal.

74
00:04:27,930 --> 00:04:29,710
Je peux t'aider.

75
